- What are you doing here?
- Huh?

783
01:00:06,604 --> 01:00:07,563
Hi, Man-ji

784
01:00:07,605 --> 01:00:10,941
Did I scare you?
Did you do something wrong?

785
01:00:11,442 --> 01:00:14,028
I was thinking about something

786
01:00:17,740 --> 01:00:20,618
So, you knew Cheon-ji?

787
01:00:24,538 --> 01:00:26,498
I heard... I'm sorry

788
01:00:35,382 --> 01:00:36,967
Why are you looking at me
like that?

789
01:00:38,302 --> 01:00:40,095
You think my hair's funny, too?

790
01:00:43,474 --> 01:00:44,683
Are you crazy?

791
01:00:44,683 --> 01:00:45,726
I just uh...

792
01:00:49,063 --> 01:00:51,357
Cheon-ji used to nag at me
to cut my hair

793
01:00:51,357 --> 01:00:53,108
but I never showed her this

794
01:00:55,277 --> 01:00:56,362
You can take a look for her

795
01:00:56,362 --> 01:00:58,572
What happened?

796
01:00:59,782 --> 01:01:05,537
There was a fire when I was little
Goes all the way down the back

797
01:01:06,872 --> 01:01:10,959
My nickname was a monster

798
01:01:12,670 --> 01:01:15,673
I left school and
started growing my hair

799
01:01:16,840 --> 01:01:18,300
I'm sorry

800
01:01:23,847 --> 01:01:30,688
So, you used to hang out with her
What did you talk about?

801
01:01:32,439 --> 01:01:35,025
She hated studying

802
01:01:35,359 --> 01:01:36,944
She loved studying

803
01:01:38,612 --> 01:01:40,072
No, she hated it

804
01:01:40,155 --> 01:01:43,325
Why do you work so hard
if you hate studying?

805
01:01:43,659 --> 01:01:47,621
People don't believe you
unless you have good grades

806
01:01:48,205 --> 01:01:52,209
Otherwise, your words just
get disintegrated in the air

807
01:01:53,419 --> 01:01:55,379
Maybe I talked too much

808
01:01:55,587 --> 01:01:59,633
No, please
Anything else?

809
01:02:01,051 --> 01:02:02,386
What are you reading?

810
01:02:02,803 --> 01:02:04,012
Hi

811
01:02:07,808 --> 01:02:09,560
Overcoming depression?

812
01:02:09,727 --> 01:02:17,735
There's this girl in my class
I'll give her the list of symptoms

813
01:02:18,068 --> 01:02:21,530
If she acts opposite to the list,
no one will suspect her

814
01:02:22,322 --> 01:02:24,116
Why would she do that?

815
01:02:24,867 --> 01:02:32,332
Her friends will leave her
if they find out she's depressed

816
01:02:32,875 --> 01:02:35,753
She hid her depression...
for some lousy friends?

817
01:02:39,047 --> 01:02:41,925
People who have friends naturally
don't understand

818
01:02:43,427 --> 01:02:49,600
At her age, friends make up
half of their entire world

819
01:02:51,769 --> 01:02:55,230
How close were you
with my sister?

820
01:02:55,314 --> 01:02:58,317
How can you know the things
that even a family didn't know?

821
01:02:58,984 --> 01:03:05,115
Sometimes, you speak
your heart out to strangers

822
01:03:06,617 --> 01:03:10,537
Stranger don't dwell
on your secrets

823
01:03:12,831 --> 01:03:14,958
I was that stranger to her

824
01:03:17,795 --> 01:03:20,923
Where was I all that time...?

825
01:03:20,964 --> 01:03:25,844
Don't be hard on yourself
Families aren't supposed to know

826
01:03:26,720 --> 01:03:33,268
Not knowing everything
helps you stick together for life

827
01:03:33,685 --> 01:03:40,359
What kind of will is no will?

828
01:03:42,486 --> 01:03:45,322
Is it 'don't ask'?

829
01:03:45,906 --> 01:03:48,283
Or 'please hear me out...'

830
01:03:50,494 --> 01:03:53,956
It kills me
because I don't know

831
01:03:58,836 --> 01:04:01,713
Didn't I make the perfect
eggs this morning?

832
01:04:03,006 --> 01:04:04,508
I hated uncooked yolk

833
01:04:04,508 --> 01:04:07,219
- Just have it, will you?
- I said no

834
01:04:08,095 --> 01:04:11,890
God... where did you get
that coldness from?

835
01:04:15,060 --> 01:04:20,315
Cheon-ji was always lovely
She always knew how I felt

836
01:04:22,317 --> 01:04:25,153
Why didn't you be nice to her
while she was around?

837
01:04:26,697 --> 01:04:27,614
What?

838
01:04:27,614 --> 01:04:32,578
We didn't pay attention
when she was struggling

839
01:04:36,373 --> 01:04:41,044
They say you bury your child
in your heart

840
01:04:41,545 --> 01:04:44,631
but I think you just
put it all behind you

841
01:04:46,842 --> 01:04:48,343
What could I do?

842
01:04:49,344 --> 01:04:54,892
You can pour cement and
smelting iron over it

843
01:04:55,058 --> 01:04:58,645
You still can't put it
behind you

844
01:04:58,729 --> 01:05:01,982
You can never bury them
because you feel sorry

845
01:05:02,065 --> 01:05:03,692
and because you can't forget

846
01:05:06,236 --> 01:05:08,071
Don't eat the damn eggs

847
01:05:16,496 --> 01:05:17,998
How can I help you?

848
01:05:18,123 --> 01:05:20,500
- How can I help you?
- How can I help you?

849
01:05:20,584 --> 01:05:22,085
Yes, ma'am... sir

850
01:05:22,169 --> 01:05:24,296
- Yes, ma'am... sir
- Yes, ma'am... sir

851
01:05:24,379 --> 01:05:26,590
Enjoy Shopping with us

852
01:05:26,715 --> 01:05:29,217
- Enjoy shopping with us
- Enjoy shopping with us

853
01:05:29,217 --> 01:05:30,928
Smile, everyone

854
01:05:31,094 --> 01:05:33,013
- Smile
- Smile

855
01:05:40,020 --> 01:05:42,898
Ma'am, have a taste of fresh tofu

856
01:05:50,280 --> 01:05:52,032
What are you doing here?

857
01:05:52,783 --> 01:05:54,826
I was just passing

858
01:05:56,370 --> 01:05:57,913
Why were passing here?

859
01:05:57,996 --> 01:05:59,873
Why not?

860
01:06:02,793 --> 01:06:06,672
Hey, 'Dumpling'! Boil some
dumplings for my daughter?

861
01:06:07,422 --> 01:06:11,093
I just put everything away
Can't you just fry some tofu?

862
01:06:11,760 --> 01:06:14,429
I want dumplings
Just do it

863
01:06:14,471 --> 01:06:16,306
Oh, come on

864
01:06:18,392 --> 01:06:20,769
How do I look?

865
01:06:22,479 --> 01:06:24,022
Pretty

866
01:06:25,732 --> 01:06:27,150
It's little too big

867
01:06:28,235 --> 01:06:30,404
Man-ji said I have to wear it
until I graduate

868
01:06:30,821 --> 01:06:32,322
What if you don't grow big?

869
01:06:33,031 --> 01:06:34,366
I hope I will

870
01:06:39,746 --> 01:06:43,875
Shall we call Man-ji and
get dinner together? Sushi?

871
01:06:47,504 --> 01:06:49,798
- <i>What?</i>
- Where <i>are you?</i>

872
01:06:49,840 --> 01:06:51,174
<i>I'm busy. Gotta go</i>

873
01:06:52,342 --> 01:06:57,014
I would've frozen to death
if it wasn't for you

874
01:06:57,848 --> 01:07:01,143
How pretty you are!
I heard you're top of the class

875
01:07:01,393 --> 01:07:03,103
Your mom can't stop
bragging about you

876
01:07:03,395 --> 01:07:05,856
- Here you go, princess
- Thank you

877
01:07:05,856 --> 01:07:09,401
Your mom's in a good mood
You can tell her anything you want

878
01:07:11,445 --> 01:07:14,573
I want her to stop being lonely

879
01:07:19,578 --> 01:07:21,955
Maybe I should start dating again

880
01:07:22,289 --> 01:07:23,999
I'm totally supportive of that

881
01:07:25,876 --> 01:07:28,336
Aren't you the sweetest

882
01:07:28,754 --> 01:07:32,090
Come on, there's gotta
be something you want?

883
01:07:32,507 --> 01:07:34,051
What I want?

884
01:07:39,765 --> 01:07:41,349
A chair for her

885
01:07:47,689 --> 01:07:51,485
Let's get some tampons
I know you've been stealing from me

886
01:07:51,568 --> 01:07:53,403
That's fine
Just come home early

887
01:07:54,529 --> 01:07:57,741
I'll stay up

888
01:08:02,370 --> 01:08:04,831
Man-ji...

889
01:08:05,624 --> 01:08:07,959
you touch my heart
when I didn't expect

890
01:08:15,509 --> 01:08:18,303
I don't know
It happens outside my door

891
01:08:18,386 --> 01:08:22,474
Only our plates are stolen

892
01:08:23,642 --> 01:08:26,728
Are you accusing me?

893
01:08:26,812 --> 01:08:30,065
I ordered from you
because we're neighbors

894
01:08:30,065 --> 01:08:33,944
It's just that... for some reason,
our plates have been going missing

895
01:08:34,027 --> 01:08:36,780
We get tons of complaints
about our food, too

896
01:08:36,905 --> 01:08:39,199
What would I do with
your delivery plates?

897
01:08:40,158 --> 01:08:42,536
They make great flowerpot holders

898
01:08:42,536 --> 01:08:44,287
I don't keep any plant
in my apartment

899
01:08:44,788 --> 01:08:45,914
I'm sorry

900
01:08:45,956 --> 01:08:48,959
I'm worried about customers
dropping out by the dozens

901
01:08:49,042 --> 01:08:51,253
Who's stealing the delivery plates?

902
01:08:51,503 --> 01:08:53,797
That's the least of our concern

903
01:08:54,005 --> 01:08:58,552
There is a rumor that we use
rotten ingredients

904
01:08:58,552 --> 01:09:00,470
Who's been saying such things?

905
01:09:00,470 --> 01:09:02,389
I think I might know

906
01:09:06,309 --> 01:09:09,521
I love eating dumplings
and feeding them to others

907
01:09:11,356 --> 01:09:13,150
Oh dear

908
01:09:19,990 --> 01:09:21,658
- Really?
- Why won't people buy more dumplings?

909
01:09:22,200 --> 01:09:23,076
It's really good

910
01:09:23,076 --> 01:09:25,537
It makes a perfect
healthy snack for everyone

911
01:09:39,926 --> 01:09:43,221
Mom, I don't feel well

912
01:09:43,346 --> 01:09:44,431
Where?

913
01:09:45,599 --> 01:09:50,145
My stomach hurts
Can I skip school today?

914
01:09:51,855 --> 01:09:54,024
You have to go to school anyway

915
01:09:54,482 --> 01:09:57,694
If it gets really bad,
go to the nurse's office

916
01:09:59,779 --> 01:10:02,157
How come you always
lose your gym uniforms?

917
01:10:03,825 --> 01:10:05,076
Yes, speaking

918
01:10:05,160 --> 01:10:09,539
<i>I don't know if this is appropriate
but there's a girl called Hwa-yeon</i>

919
01:10:09,539 --> 01:10:12,167
<i>who seems to pick on Cheon-ji</i>

920
01:10:12,250 --> 01:10:14,252
<i>Maybe it's best to pull them apart</i>

921
01:10:14,252 --> 01:10:15,503
I see

922
01:10:15,879 --> 01:10:19,216
Let the kids sort it out
between themselves

923
01:10:21,343 --> 01:10:25,513
You should raise your child
to be clever, not cunning

924
01:10:26,056 --> 01:10:27,557
What?

925
01:10:27,849 --> 01:10:31,811
It's your fault that
you raised yours meek

926
01:10:33,980 --> 01:10:35,523
Please leave, I'm busy

927
01:10:39,361 --> 01:10:42,572
Shall we order black bean noodles
for dinner?

928
01:10:44,282 --> 01:10:48,870
I hate black bean noodles
more than anything in the world

929
01:10:49,412 --> 01:10:54,292
Okay...
let's boil some ramen then

930
01:10:54,668 --> 01:11:00,298
I'll die because of
black bean noodles

931
01:11:18,650 --> 01:11:19,859
Mom

932
01:11:21,611 --> 01:11:23,113
What's wrong?

933
01:11:27,826 --> 01:11:29,160
Mom?

934
01:11:31,913 --> 01:11:34,958
God, you're boiling!
Wait for me, okay?

935
01:11:42,257 --> 01:11:43,550
Hello?

936
01:11:45,593 --> 01:11:47,929
Hello, is anyone there?

937
01:11:52,851 --> 01:11:55,812
Are you alright?

938
01:11:57,480 --> 01:11:58,898
I'm okay

939
01:12:00,859 --> 01:12:02,152
You sure?

940
01:12:02,152 --> 01:12:03,320
Yeah

941
01:12:05,447 --> 01:12:07,615
What are you doing here?

942
01:12:08,825 --> 01:12:11,244
Why couldn't you
find this yourself?

943
01:12:14,331 --> 01:12:15,749
Look in there

944
01:12:16,041 --> 01:12:17,083
What?

945
01:12:17,500 --> 01:12:21,546
There is a note
that Cheon-ji left

946
01:12:34,476 --> 01:12:37,062
<i>My dearest sister
who I've always envied</i>

947
01:12:37,437 --> 01:12:40,940
<i>Don't forget me even if
I go to a faraway place</i>

948
01:12:41,524 --> 01:12:43,193
<i>I love you, sis</i>

949
01:12:44,194 --> 01:12:47,405
<i>Second of five sealed yarns</i>

950
01:12:49,949 --> 01:12:51,701
Why didn't you tell me?

951
01:12:52,035 --> 01:12:54,037
I'm telling you now

952
01:12:57,040 --> 01:12:59,876
It's the second one of five

953
01:13:00,710 --> 01:13:02,796
It means there are more

954
01:13:07,592 --> 01:13:09,302
Because I didn't have this...

955
01:13:18,395 --> 01:13:22,190
Thank you, Cheon-ji

956
01:13:23,942 --> 01:13:25,193
Cheonji

957
01:13:35,328 --> 01:13:36,913
Can I get a black bean noodle?

958
01:13:38,164 --> 01:13:39,833
One black noodle for here

959
01:13:42,168 --> 01:13:45,839
It's pretty quiet
Maybe because it's a weekday

960
01:13:46,714 --> 01:13:50,343
With this economy,
it's no different in the weekend

961
01:13:52,595 --> 01:13:56,933
I just moved and I didn't
come around to say hello properly

962
01:14:11,489 --> 01:14:13,199
Have a drink?

963
01:14:14,117 --> 01:14:15,410
Why not

964
01:14:22,959 --> 01:14:26,504
I heard about what happened

965
01:14:27,255 --> 01:14:31,801
I sit here all day but
news carries itself here

966
01:14:36,139 --> 01:14:38,057
You must be devastated

967
01:14:39,350 --> 01:14:43,646
but maybe it wasn't her fate
to have a long life

968
01:14:45,190 --> 01:14:48,860
I think her destined life
was average

969
01:14:50,445 --> 01:14:52,947
until someone shortened it for her

970
01:15:01,414 --> 01:15:03,041
I came to give you this

971
01:15:06,878 --> 01:15:10,173
My daughter wanted to
give this to Hwa-yeon

972
01:15:10,924 --> 01:15:16,971
It would've been nice
if she could give it herself

973
01:15:18,348 --> 01:15:20,600
I hope your daughter likes it

974
01:15:24,062 --> 01:15:26,105
The noodle's on the house

975
01:15:26,105 --> 01:15:28,858
- No, thank you
- Cheon-ji's mom...

976
01:15:28,858 --> 01:15:31,319
Don't!
If you're going to apologize

977
01:15:35,031 --> 01:15:37,158
An apology in words

978
01:15:41,037 --> 01:15:43,915
is acceptable only
when you can forgive

979
01:15:44,249 --> 01:15:46,459
If you get an apology
you can't accept

980
01:15:51,381 --> 01:15:53,132
it'll only stab you in the heart

981
01:15:54,509 --> 01:16:00,557
Especially when I have
no intention of hearing

982
01:16:02,475 --> 01:16:07,564
It's just a convenient excuse
for you to hide behind

983
01:16:08,231 --> 01:16:11,234
'I apologized but
she didn't accept it'

984
01:16:14,404 --> 01:16:16,406
That's what you're gonna say

985
01:16:28,251 --> 01:16:33,381
I'm sorry but I can't
pass this to my daughter

986
01:17:08,166 --> 01:17:13,171
Now you know
why I moved here

987
01:17:16,633 --> 01:17:19,510
I want you to look at my face
for the rest of your lives

988
01:17:44,160 --> 01:17:45,703
Chinese restaurant

989
01:17:46,287 --> 01:17:50,500
Oh, hello... sorry?

990
01:17:52,543 --> 01:17:59,050
Hwa-yeon fell ill
So, she's taking a rest at home

991
01:17:59,133 --> 01:18:02,053
I'll send her as soon
ass he feels betters

992
01:18:02,178 --> 01:18:10,353
Please understand
if she acts strangely

993
01:18:10,853 --> 01:18:15,525
The dead girl's mother
moved here on purpose

994
01:18:17,527 --> 01:18:19,278
Of course, she can't have

995
01:18:19,278 --> 01:18:22,907
Okay... thank you

996
01:18:23,616 --> 01:18:27,120
Was that her teacher?
She skipped school?

997
01:18:28,079 --> 01:18:31,999
How can you be so uninterested?

998
01:18:32,083 --> 01:18:35,461
She's so full of silly thoughts
in her head

999
01:18:35,461 --> 01:18:37,046
I'm gonna teach her a lesson

1000
01:18:37,130 --> 01:18:40,341
Will you just shut up?

1001
01:18:46,264 --> 01:18:47,640
Oh, God!

1002
01:19:06,117 --> 01:19:08,286
<i>You used to knit</i>

1003
01:19:08,661 --> 01:19:10,246
This is for you

1004
01:19:13,124 --> 01:19:15,418
How are you feeling?

1005
01:19:16,085 --> 01:19:17,336
Better

1006
01:19:24,927 --> 01:19:27,180
Shall we start?

1007
01:19:28,514 --> 01:19:30,600
It's still break time

1008
01:19:31,100 --> 01:19:33,519
Alright...
I'll just leave the books here

1009
01:19:33,603 --> 01:19:36,230
I wanted to spend more
time with you, that's all

1010
01:19:37,774 --> 01:19:38,858
Miss Lee

1011
01:19:39,025 --> 01:19:39,942
Yes'?

1012
01:19:40,026 --> 01:19:44,906
I'm not feeling well
Can I sit in the front?

1013
01:19:45,948 --> 01:19:48,117
Who wants to switch seats
for Hwa-yeon?

1014
01:19:48,743 --> 01:19:50,244
I will

1015
01:19:50,536 --> 01:19:54,081
Okay, I'll see you
when the break is over

1016
01:19:57,627 --> 01:20:00,671
Thanks...
This is for you

1017
01:20:10,515 --> 01:20:11,933
What are you making?

1018
01:20:12,308 --> 01:20:13,976
A sitting mat

1019
01:20:13,976 --> 01:20:15,478
Will you make one for me?

1020
01:20:15,853 --> 01:20:17,230
Are you crazy?

1021
01:20:24,445 --> 01:20:26,989
- Where are you going?
- She's upset because of you

1022
01:20:26,989 --> 01:20:28,616
What did I do?

1023
01:20:29,283 --> 01:20:33,412
Oh, forget it

1024
01:20:36,249 --> 01:20:38,167
Did we have homework
for this class?

1025
01:20:39,627 --> 01:20:42,046
Why come all the way here
to ask that?

1026
01:20:46,384 --> 01:20:48,678
Wanna go to the restroom with me?

1027
01:20:48,928 --> 01:20:52,515
No, Mi-so had to move
because of you

1028
01:20:52,640 --> 01:20:55,101
I'm sorry but
I couldn't see the board

1029
01:20:55,184 --> 01:20:58,020
It's always the dumb ones
that complain about the board

1030
01:21:07,071 --> 01:21:10,032
I can't take it anymore
I should go home

1031
01:21:23,504 --> 01:21:26,048
- Talk to her for me?
- Yes, miss

1032
01:21:26,299 --> 01:21:27,925
Okay

1033
01:21:34,765 --> 01:21:37,894
That's my yarn, miss

1034
01:21:40,438 --> 01:21:42,231
Don't knit during the class

1035
01:21:42,356 --> 01:21:46,986
I wasn't
I just had it out on the desk

1036
01:21:47,486 --> 01:21:48,738
Is it a scarf?

1037
01:21:49,655 --> 01:21:52,575
Just a wide plane

1038
01:21:52,742 --> 01:21:54,285
Alright, you can go now

1039
01:22:11,969 --> 01:22:14,263
So, you're just knitting
a square shape?

1040
01:22:16,140 --> 01:22:19,101
Did Miss Lee ask you
to talk to me?

1041
01:22:19,143 --> 01:22:22,063
No... to Miso

1042
01:22:22,480 --> 01:22:25,066
