1080
01:26:40,654 --> 01:26:45,367
Did you say that your mom
worked in GS Mart?

1081
01:26:45,993 --> 01:26:48,913
Yeah... why?

1082
01:26:49,538 --> 01:26:50,956
Nothing

1083
01:26:53,042 --> 01:26:58,547
