1100
01:28:17,501 --> 01:28:19,128
I see... thank you

1101
01:28:19,211 --> 01:28:21,171
Cheon-ji's mom

1102
01:28:23,465 --> 01:28:25,801
Get out of here
before I call the police

1103
01:28:25,801 --> 01:28:26,844
Who is he?

1104
01:28:26,927 --> 01:28:28,053
Go inside

1105
01:28:28,053 --> 01:28:29,805
You must be Man-ji

1106
01:28:29,888 --> 01:28:31,140
