What you saw what that shit

1146
01:30:49,111 --> 01:30:50,946
Are you okay?

1147
01:30:51,321 --> 01:30:54,950
As you can see, I'm fine

1148
01:30:55,159 --> 01:30:57,578
How did you end up seeing
someone like that?

1149
01:30:57,870 --> 01:30:59,621
You must have pretty low standards

1150
01:31:08,797 --> 01:31:10,549
Just kidding

1151
01:31:17,931 --> 01:31:21,059
This coffee's really good
Is it Maxim?

1152
01:31:23,020 --> 01:31:25,772
Shall I give you a trim?
Maybe like this?

1153
01:31:25,981 --> 01:31:26,857
What's the matter?

1154
01:31:26,857 --> 01:31:28,400
Time for shampoo

1155
01:31:46,168 --> 01:31:47,002
Here

1156
01:31:48,170 --> 01:31:50,172
Thank you

1157
01:31:50,839 --> 01:31:52,716
You haven't had a proper
homemade meal in a while

1158
01:31:54,009 --> 01:31:57,179
It's not much but
it'll taste alright

1159
01:32:04,770 --> 01:32:06,813
Does your dad
come home often?

1160
01:32:07,773 --> 01:32:10,859
He doesn't seem like
the type to care

1161
01:32:13,111 --> 01:32:15,531
You used to come to
the store I work in

1162
01:32:15,906 --> 01:32:19,243
I could tell you're used
to grocery shopping

1163
01:32:19,576 --> 01:32:21,870
You know, I faltered briefly

1164
01:32:23,038 --> 01:32:24,706
thinking about you girls

1165
01:32:24,706 --> 01:32:27,751
Shall I bite the bullet
for the sake of the girls?

1166
01:32:30,254 --> 01:32:34,049
But after Cheon-ji passed,
I realized how silly I was

1167
01:32:34,174 --> 01:32:36,218
I couldn't even
look after my child

1168
01:32:39,888 --> 01:32:43,892
They say all the wrong doings of the parents
are passed down to their children

1169
01:32:46,395 --> 01:32:49,231
I don't know how he treats you

1170
01:32:49,273 --> 01:32:52,985
but he shouldn't have done that
to me or to your mother

1171
01:32:53,235 --> 01:32:57,239
He doesn't know
what he's doing wrong

1172
01:32:58,574 --> 01:33:00,826
We're doing fine on our own

1173
01:33:01,243 --> 01:33:04,621
I know, I can see that now

1174
01:33:05,414 --> 01:33:07,791
Your mother did a good job
raising you

1175
01:33:08,834 --> 01:33:10,252
Come on, eat up

1176
01:33:17,426 --> 01:33:21,054
Mi-ra, don't take the trouble
to go to other grocery store

1177
01:33:21,305 --> 01:33:23,599
Ours is the best in this area

1178
01:33:24,433 --> 01:33:28,770
You can't avoid or block out
someone forever by trying

1179
01:33:28,854 --> 01:33:32,065
And there is no need to
forgive or love everyone

1180
01:33:32,149 --> 01:33:36,778
Just let yourself feel
what you feel

1181
01:33:41,992 --> 01:33:43,368
What's wrong, sweetie?

1182
01:33:46,079 --> 01:33:54,421
You seem like a lot better person
than I thought, but my dad...

1183
01:33:57,591 --> 01:34:02,346
She must be over whelmed
by a proper home cooking

1184
01:34:04,056 --> 01:34:06,975
Eat up
Clean out your plate

1185
01:34:11,021 --> 01:34:12,105
Mom

1186
01:34:12,481 --> 01:34:15,525
Didn't you say you look
at the face in a man?

1187
01:34:15,651 --> 01:34:16,693
Yeah

1188
01:34:19,488 --> 01:34:22,032
My dad's not exactly...

1189
01:34:24,660 --> 01:34:31,708
You guys don't know
That's the look that ruled the 80's

1190
01:34:44,012 --> 01:34:45,222
What's this?

1191
01:34:50,143 --> 01:34:52,104
Hwa-yeon, that crazy bitch

1192
01:34:53,522 --> 01:34:54,856
Did Hwa-yeon give it to you?

1193
01:34:54,856 --> 01:34:56,108
Yeah

1194
01:34:56,692 --> 01:34:57,943
Can I have it?

1195
01:34:58,026 --> 01:35:02,531
Whatever!
This is so annoying

1196
01:35:05,909 --> 01:35:07,619
Hey, what brings you here?

1197
01:35:07,828 --> 01:35:11,206
Do you have the ball of yarn
that I gave you earlier?

1198
01:35:11,373 --> 01:35:14,334
It's probably still in my locker
Why?

1199
01:35:14,376 --> 01:35:18,130
This note was in the yarn ball
that Cheon-ji gave Hwa-yeon

1200
01:35:21,341 --> 01:35:23,969
You really can't be separated

1201
01:35:28,056 --> 01:35:29,391
Where did you get this?

1202
01:35:29,391 --> 01:35:32,811
It was in the yarn ball
that Cheon-ji gave Hwa-yeon

1203
01:35:34,062 --> 01:35:35,605
Do you know about this?

1204
01:35:35,897 --> 01:35:41,069
Why do you have it, not Hwa-yeon?
Where is she?

1205
01:35:41,153 --> 01:35:43,113
She hasn't been
coming to school much

1206
01:35:43,238 --> 01:35:46,450
So, the yarn ball you gave me...
Cheon-ji gave it to you?

1207
01:35:54,458 --> 01:35:58,879
'A murderer in the making'
That's a warning, isn't it?

1208
01:36:00,297 --> 01:36:02,758
Hwa-yeon won't lift an eyebrow

1209
01:36:02,966 --> 01:36:06,595
Wasn't it fun for all of you?

1210
01:36:09,848 --> 01:36:11,433
Are you coming, too?

1211
01:36:11,600 --> 01:36:12,809
Yeah

1212
01:36:13,351 --> 01:36:15,270
Is there nothing
you want to ask me?

1213
01:36:16,229 --> 01:36:23,862
If I asked you why you bully me,
you'll say you've never done that

1214
01:36:24,112 --> 01:36:27,491
Did you bother to ask?

1215
01:36:27,991 --> 01:36:31,578
For years, she wrote three o'clock
on your invitation,

1216
01:36:31,620 --> 01:36:33,705
but you always show up at three

1217
01:36:33,955 --> 01:36:38,126
You play along when you know
that 'my sister' is you

1218
01:36:38,794 --> 01:36:42,964
You just pretended not to know
That's what scares me

1219
01:36:43,131 --> 01:36:48,094
You and Hwa-yeon both think
that you can only keep friends

1220
01:36:49,304 --> 01:36:51,890
by picking on someone

1221
01:36:53,558 --> 01:36:56,478
Do it all you want

1222
01:36:57,562 --> 01:36:59,648
I won't wince

1223
01:37:00,023 --> 01:37:05,278
I'm different from Hwa-yeon
I have reasons

1224
01:37:06,363 --> 01:37:10,742
But Hwa-yeon, she won't realize
until someone ends up dead

1225
01:37:16,665 --> 01:37:20,669
Why do you always carry
that color of yarn?

1226
01:37:26,258 --> 01:37:27,676
You...

1227
01:37:33,682 --> 01:37:39,020
What is it that you want to see?

1228
01:37:46,695 --> 01:37:49,698
No. Mi-ra should read it

1229
01:37:50,282 --> 01:37:52,450
It was meant for her

1230
01:38:06,673 --> 01:38:10,594
I'll just read it later

1231
01:38:12,762 --> 01:38:15,724
I didn't know
I really didn't know

1232
01:38:15,724 --> 01:38:17,100
Open it

1233
01:38:24,065 --> 01:38:27,068
<i>Couldn't you keep some of the thing
you said to yourself?</i>

1234
01:38:27,485 --> 01:38:30,030
<i>Sometimes the words
from your mouth</i>

1235
01:38:30,071 --> 01:38:32,741
<i>cut deep into my heart</i>

1236
01:38:33,158 --> 01:38:35,160
<i>but I'll forgive you</i>

1237
01:38:35,410 --> 01:38:38,455
<i>because I remember
the first time I saw you smile</i>

1238
01:38:43,710 --> 01:38:46,421
What did you do to her?

1239
01:38:48,298 --> 01:38:53,511
Why'd you hit me?
I've been good to her all along

1240
01:38:53,929 --> 01:38:57,682
while everyone pretended
as if she didn't exist

1241
01:38:57,766 --> 01:39:02,062
But after I saw dad with her mom

1242
01:39:02,437 --> 01:39:04,606
I couldn't forgive her

1243
01:39:05,649 --> 01:39:10,028
Who does she think she is
to forgive me?

1244
01:39:10,028 --> 01:39:11,446
Are you crazy?

1245
01:39:11,613 --> 01:39:13,990
- Why drag dad into this?
- Shut up!

1246
01:39:18,787 --> 01:39:21,790
Did you play her?

1247
01:39:21,873 --> 01:39:25,627
It's not like that...

1248
01:39:27,629 --> 01:39:28,797
I'm sorry

1249
01:39:28,922 --> 01:39:30,799
Did you play her like a goddamn toy?

1250
01:39:30,799 --> 01:39:32,425
Stop it, Man-ji

1251
01:39:34,010 --> 01:39:36,721
Mi-ra was one of few
who were nice to her

1252
01:39:36,930 --> 01:39:40,558
Then, she got mad after
seeing our parent together

1253
01:39:41,267 --> 01:39:44,688
It was one fight
How can anyone...

1254
01:39:46,314 --> 01:39:47,816
die over it?

1255
01:39:51,152 --> 01:39:52,320
I'm sorry...

1256
01:39:54,114 --> 01:39:57,492
I know how you feel

1257
01:39:58,410 --> 01:40:01,246
but if you have something
to say to my sister

1258
01:40:01,997 --> 01:40:04,124
talk to me
Don't yell at her

1259
01:40:07,002 --> 01:40:08,336
Let's go, Mi-ra

1260
01:40:20,890 --> 01:40:24,352
You're so good, I hate you

1261
01:40:29,441 --> 01:40:31,443
She's not going to college?

1262
01:40:31,735 --> 01:40:37,532
She gave up college and
wanted to move to a vocational class

1263
01:40:38,867 --> 01:40:46,207
but after what happened to her sister,
she changed her mind

1264
01:40:46,458 --> 01:40:48,334
She says she wants to
go to a good college

1265
01:40:50,837 --> 01:40:55,842
With her grades, she can apply
to any college of her choice

1266
01:40:55,925 --> 01:40:56,885
I see

1267
01:40:57,052 --> 01:40:59,804
If you look here...

1268
01:41:41,930 --> 01:41:43,098
AAC

1269
01:41:44,140 --> 01:41:45,642
AAB

1270
01:41:50,438 --> 01:41:52,107
How beautiful you are

1271
01:41:55,610 --> 01:41:58,113
Please don't die early

1272
01:42:33,481 --> 01:42:35,984
You know the Chinese restaurant
outside Chowon Apartments

1273
01:42:36,025 --> 01:42:38,403
They got busted for using
out of date flour

1274
01:42:39,028 --> 01:42:41,990
