by torturing someone?

1284
01:43:35,335 --> 01:43:39,255
This is the only way we'll move
After the restaurant shuts down

1285
01:43:41,216 --> 01:43:43,176
Why are you doing this to me?

1286
01:43:44,928 --> 01:43:46,262
Why?

1287
01:43:48,223 --> 01:43:52,060
Why? Everyone else except you
will know why, bitch!

1288
01:43:53,186 --> 01:43:54,938
Why did you do it to Cheon-ji?

1289
01:43:55,188 --> 01:43:57,565
