1290
01:43:59,609 --> 01:44:04,572
You can kill yourself over nothing
She was a freak all along

1291
01:44:05,907 --> 01:44:09,577
Everyone says that about her
Where could she go?

1292
01:44:09,661 --> 01:44:12,914
How is she supposed to say
how much she suffered

1293
01:44:13,414 --> 01:44:17,627
how broken and torn she was

1294
01:44:21,130 --> 01:44:22,966
I hate going to school

1295
01:44:24,926 --> 01:44:27,595
I hate it so much
that I'm gonna go crazy

1296
01:44:28,596 --> 01:44:30,640
And Cheon-ji's not there anymore

1297
01:44:32,934 --> 01:44:36,896
No one believe me
when I say this

1298
01:44:37,772 --> 01:44:40,024
No one!

1299
01:44:42,193 --> 01:44:44,279
But I miss her, too

1300
01:44:46,781 --> 01:44:48,658
I really miss her

1301
01:44:53,246 --> 01:44:54,664
You, crazy bitch

1302
01:45:14,809 --> 01:45:16,144
Let's go

1303
01:45:18,229 --> 01:45:19,480
Man-ji

1304
01:45:19,605 --> 01:45:22,817
Come on. It's dangerous
to be by yourself here

1305
01:45:28,781 --> 01:45:30,700
I'm so sorry
Forgive me

1306
01:45:38,708 --> 01:45:40,877
Cheon-ji left this for you

1307
01:45:55,933 --> 01:45:59,228
<i>I'll forgive you before I go</i>

1308
01:46:00,021 --> 01:46:04,192
<i>Because you'll still be here
after I'm gone</i>

1309
01:46:05,234 --> 01:46:09,280
<i>I wish you won't do it again</i>

1310
01:46:10,365 --> 01:46:14,160
<i>I wish you won't suffer no more</i>

1311
01:46:16,996 --> 01:46:19,499
Don't manipulate people
from now

1312
01:46:20,083 --> 01:46:23,169
No matter what glittery things
you have in your hands

1313
01:46:23,544 --> 01:46:27,340
It's nothing to those who
doesn't care about them

1314
01:46:29,008 --> 01:46:30,718
And I will make sure

1315
01:46:31,386 --> 01:46:35,181
that you don't wear out
and follow my sister's path

1316
01:46:36,808 --> 01:46:38,810
Not because I like you

1317
01:46:38,893 --> 01:46:44,273
but because I can't let my sister
take blames even after she died

1318
01:46:46,734 --> 01:46:48,694
I start now

1319
01:46:49,153 --> 01:46:51,656
until I find her
last ball of yarn

1320
01:46:54,575 --> 01:46:56,077
Let's go home

1321
01:47:56,220 --> 01:47:58,139
<i>I'm sorry for leaving early</i>

1322
01:47:58,973 --> 01:48:01,476
<i>I'll eat well wherever I go</i>

1323
01:48:02,560 --> 01:48:08,649
<i>So, promise me that
you'll be strong</i>

1324
01:48:09,692 --> 01:48:13,070
<i>or I'll be very sad</i>

1325
01:48:14,906 --> 01:48:17,658
<i>I love you, mom</i>

1326
01:48:24,540 --> 01:48:29,545
I love you, too, Cheon-ji

1327
01:50:48,726 --> 01:50:50,394
Were you waiting for me?

1328
01:50:54,815 --> 01:50:58,653
I'm so tired
Give me a piggyback ride?

1329
01:50:59,320 --> 01:51:00,988
You will?

1330
01:51:02,448 --> 01:51:05,201
Oh, I am so happy!
You come to me

1331
01:51:08,162 --> 01:51:13,250
You cold-hearted brat
Wait! Stop

1332
01:51:14,835 --> 01:51:16,879
Only because you're
embarrassing me

1333
01:51:19,507 --> 01:51:21,217
Don't push it, mom

1334
01:51:32,103 --> 01:51:33,270
Come on

1335
01:51:35,189 --> 01:51:36,774
It's awkward

1336
01:51:37,024 --> 01:51:38,192
As you like

1337
01:51:45,700 --> 01:51:46,784
Mom

1338
01:51:47,535 --> 01:51:49,370
Cheon-ji was in my dream

1339
01:51:51,372 --> 01:51:52,790
Was she smiling?

1340
01:51:53,332 --> 01:51:58,796
The widest smile...
We gave her a big hug

1341
01:52:00,756 --> 01:52:04,260
She must be doing well

1342
01:52:42,214 --> 01:52:45,676
<i>My dear little sister,</i>

1343
01:52:46,635 --> 01:52:50,264
<i>you've always been
the sweetest sister</i>

1344
01:52:52,349 --> 01:52:56,270
<i>I won't forget you
no matter how far away you are</i>

1345
01:52:58,105 --> 01:53:01,150
<i>I love you, sis</i>

1346
01:53:38,062 --> 01:53:39,814
<i>I hope you're well and happy</i>

1347
01:53:40,481 --> 01:53:43,692
<i>It was nothing after a while,
isn't it?</i>

1348
01:53:45,486 --> 01:53:48,948
<i>Thank you for pulling through it</i>
